²�����������Y�L�y�ѦҤ��m�z���ޥΡA�N�O�׭z�L�ھڪ��峹�A�ʥF���ȡC�ѦҤ��m�ޥΤ��d�ҡG(�`�N�G�W�L��ӥH�W�h�Hdash�s��)State space averaging techniques are commonly used in the analysis and control design of pulse width modulated (PWM) 
